In this section we will cover *FluentisInstaller* WebApi installation for *Windows* and *Linux* operating systems.

:::info
Some IP addresses, folders, configurations, DNS names are used for illustrative purposes only.
:::

:::warning
***FluentisInstaller* must be installed on each servers** involved in the Fluentis installion process (i.e. all the servers that host SQL Server installations or fluentis apps installations) **and properly registered** inside the  **FluentisLiveUpdate** web app, under **Installer Services** page. 
:::